        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[马斯克旗下 AI 聊天机器人 Grok 已向美国所有 X Premium+用户推出]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>马斯克推出的 AI 聊天机器人 Grok，其 beta 测试版本已向美国 X Premium+ 订阅者推出。预计再一星期会扩展到所有英语用户。然后是第二大用户群的日语版本，希望到 2024 年初就能扩展到所有语言。马斯克预期，在一开始会出现很多问题，但他们每天都会快速改善，也感谢用户的积极回馈。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Grok AI (beta) is now rolled out to all 𝕏 Premium+ subscribers in the US.</p><p>There will be many issues at first, but expect rapid improvement almost every day. Your feedback is much appreciated.</p><p>Will expand to all English language users in about a week or so. Japanese is next…</p><p>— Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1733077220602589594?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 8, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_60 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/elon-musk-grok-ai-rolling-out-to-all-x-premium-in-us#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-657688974f9ad"><span class=""><span class="eztoc-hide" style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-657688974f9ad"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/elon-musk-grok-ai-rolling-out-to-all-x-premium-in-us/#%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%BD%E9%BB%98%E7%9A%84_AI_%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA_Grok" title="最幽默的 AI 聊天机器人 Grok">最幽默的 AI 聊天机器人 Grok</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/elon-musk-grok-ai-rolling-out-to-all-x-premium-in-us/#Grok_%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E3%80%8CFun_Mode%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8CRegular_Mode%E3%80%8D" title="Grok 提供「Fun Mode」和「Regular Mode」">Grok 提供「Fun Mode」和「Regular Mode」</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%BD%E9%BB%98%E7%9A%84_AI_%E8%81%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA_Grok"></span>最幽默的 AI 聊天机器人 Grok<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>马斯克力抗挑 ChatGPT 的 AI 聊天机器人 Grok ，在十一月初正式推出。Grok 是模仿《银河便车指南》的人工智慧，因为其可以透过 X 平台即时存取讯息，比其他模型具有更即时的巨大优势。因此几乎可以回答任何问题，而且还十分幽默。</p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/xai-grok-loves-sarcasm-and-has-current-information" target="_blank" rel="noopener">xAI 模仿《银河便车指南》的 Grok 正式启用，幽默爱讽刺还有最新时事</a>)</p><p>Grok 正式整合到 X 平台后，用户将能够透过该功能轻松找到当前流行的议题，而无需在 X 上花费数小时不停地地浏览各种推文。</p><p>像 Insider Paper 即问了「 X 的哪个帐号有最好的迷因发文？」</p><p>结果 Grok 列举了 @memes, @dankmemes, @funny 和 @meme，还不忘提醒 @elonmusk 也有许多不错的迷因梗！</p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-86080" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87_2023-12-10_125507617.png?resize=634%2C389&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="634" height="389" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_125507617.png?w=634&amp;ssl=1 634w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_125507617.png?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_125507617.png?resize=600%2C368&amp;ssl=1 600w" sizes="(max-width: 634px) 100vw, 634px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>不过 DeFi 研究员 Ignas 也担心这可能导致诈骗机器人帐户的激增、以及代币炒作或泡沫的问题发生。</p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/defi-ignas-xai-grok-twitter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">轻松追踪百倍币！Grok AI 将整合至 X (推特) 中，诈骗机器人激增成隐忧</a>)</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Grok_%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E3%80%8CFun_Mode%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8CRegular_Mode%E3%80%8D"></span>Grok 提供「Fun Mode」和「Regular Mode」<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>根据<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7NalbAvWfHY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网友的使用分享</a>，在登入 X 后，左手边即会出现 Grok 的选项，点选进去后，在右上角会有「Fun Mode」和「Regular Mode」可供选择，而预设选项为「Fun Mode」。</p><p>而在实际测试之后，发现「Fun Mode」会有些玩笑话，Grok 也会承认是他编造出来的，所以提醒用户要询问重要问题时，记得要转换为「Regular Mode」，这样的模式底下，Grok 就会帮你标注出处来源，方便用户再深入了解，不过虽然是使用「Regular Mode」，Grok 的回答仍是十分幽默。</p><p>据马斯克的推文，美国以外的英语版 Grok 将在一星期后推出，想要尝鲜的用户可密切关注！</p><p><img class="alignnone  wp-image-86081" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87_2023-12-10_134713648.png?resize=704%2C410&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="704" height="410" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_134713648.png?w=1666&amp;ssl=1 1666w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_134713648.png?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_134713648.png?resize=1024%2C596&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_134713648.png?resize=600%2C349&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_134713648.png?resize=768%2C447&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-10_134713648.png?resize=1536%2C894&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>
]]>
