                <![CDATA[比特币再创今年新高，ADA、AVAX、DOT 表现亮眼]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">昨晚公布的美国非农就业数据超乎预期，投资人对经济软著陆乐观看待。美股与加密货币皆表现亮眼，比特币再度创下今年新高，ADA、AVAX、DOT 表现亮眼！</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_60 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/crypto-update-as-of-9-dec-2023#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-6576889764a6e"><span class=""><span class="eztoc-hide" style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-6576889764a6e"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/crypto-update-as-of-9-dec-2023/#%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%B6%85%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E5%89%B5%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98" title="就业数据超好，美股创今年新高">就业数据超好，美股创今年新高</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/crypto-update-as-of-9-dec-2023/#%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8CADA%E3%80%81AVAX%E3%80%81DOT%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E4%BA%AE%E7%9C%BC" title="比特币再度创下今年新高，ADA、AVAX、DOT 表现亮眼">比特币再度创下今年新高，ADA、AVAX、DOT 表现亮眼</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%B6%85%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E5%89%B5%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98"></span>就业数据超好，美股创今年新高<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>美国劳工部昨日公布，11 月非农就业人口增加 19.9 万人，高于市场预期，主因是汽车工人结束罢工、重返工作岗位所致。失业率从 10 月触及的两年高点 3.9% 降到 3.7%，是 7 月来最低，反映更多人加入劳动市场。</p><p>S&amp;P 500 指数创下今年收盘新高点，今年上涨幅度已逾 20%。那斯达克指数上涨 63.98 点，涨幅 0.45%。道琼指数大涨 130.49 点，创下近两年来的新高！</p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-86052" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87_2023-12-09_114133562.png?resize=1312%2C377&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1312" height="377" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-09_114133562.png?w=1312&amp;ssl=1 1312w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-09_114133562.png?resize=300%2C86&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-09_114133562.png?resize=1024%2C294&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-09_114133562.png?resize=600%2C172&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/图片_2023-12-09_114133562.png?resize=768%2C221&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8CADA%E3%80%81AVAX%E3%80%81DOT%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E4%BA%AE%E7%9C%BC"></span>比特币再度创下今年新高，ADA、AVAX、DOT 表现亮眼<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>加密货币方面，比特币再度创下今年新高，一度来到 44,676，7 天涨幅已达 13.9%，今年迄今已上涨 167%。以太坊昨日则微幅下滑，但本周也有 12.4% 的亮丽表现。</p><p>ADA (Cardano) 昨日强劲上涨，创下今年新高，本周涨幅已近五成。</p><p>Avalanche (AVAX) 市值排名再度上升，根据<a href="https://abmedia.io/binance-research-as-of-nov-2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener">币安的月报</a>，Avalanche (AVAX) 的成长得益于去中心化金融协定 Benqi，其整体 TVL 在十一月增长了 16%。</p><p>波卡币 Polkadot (DOT) 昨日上涨逾 18%，挤进前十大排名，与 Polkadot 相关的 Web3 基金会最近宣布将投资 100 万美元国库券，并透过 Anemoy 代币化。Polkadot 试图为美国投资者提供短期国债投资，引发了对 DOT 代币的购买潮。</p><figure id="attachment_86051" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-86051" style="width: 1194px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-86051 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/_2023-12-09_110926897-e1702091388469.png?resize=1194%2C1068&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1194" height="1068" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/_2023-12-09_110926897-e1702091388469.png?w=1194&amp;ssl=1 1194w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/_2023-12-09_110926897-e1702091388469.png?resize=300%2C268&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/_2023-12-09_110926897-e1702091388469.png?resize=1024%2C916&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/_2023-12-09_110926897-e1702091388469.png?resize=600%2C537&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/_2023-12-09_110926897-e1702091388469.png?resize=768%2C687&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-86051" class="wp-caption-text">资料来源：CoinGecko, 统计时间：2023/12/9 11:00</figcaption></figure>
